data.description: This lakeside retreat is truly a dream come true for those seeking both relaxation and entertainment. Nestled on a picturesque lakefront lot on Lake Wildwood, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of comfort and luxury. As you step inside, you're greeted by a spacious Great Room, ideal for gatherings and socializing with friends and family. The recessed Family Room adds another dimension to the living space, providing a cozy spot for relaxation or additional entertaining space. The kitchen is beautifully appointed and ready to cater to your culinary adventures, while offering stunning views of the lake from the Great Room and Family Room. Imagine preparing delicious meals while enjoying the tranquil scenery just beyond your windows. This home features four bedrooms, ensuring ample space for everyone to rest and rejuvenate. Additionally, three additional rooms offer versatility for various needs, with a cozy small office space conveniently located off the master bedroom. Outside, the allure of summer days beckons you to the inground pool for a refreshing dip or to the dock for leisurely moments overlooking the serene lake. And for those who love boating, the easy access to the water ensures endless opportunities for adventure. With a garage that can accommodate three cars and a generously sized driveway, parking will never be an issue, even when hosting guests. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or an entertainer's paradise, this lakeside oasis is ready to welcome you home. Don't miss out on the opportunity to experience the best of lake living in this exquisite property on Lake Wildwood.
